{"tid":1102081,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我發現腦魔生得愈來愈似我個frd......","createTime":"2019-04-11T12:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T15:20:49.000Z","uid":238361,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39630d190843ced16155ddf69f5b5eade238ac5f","tid":1102081,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:38:44.000Z","msg":"話說我個frd成日喺WhatsApp用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個表情，我前排食飽飯冇屎痾就開post：<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我個frd生得愈來愈似腦魔......<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1097738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1097738</a><br />\n唔知我個frd係咪睇到我個post，呢排都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個表情，但就係咁用其他表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我先發現，原來其他表情都好似佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底腦魔係咪照住我個frd黎畫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我亦漸漸發現，自己用ig, snapchat嗰陣，冇咗腦魔，我已經唔可以準確咁表達到我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我，已經唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實際上，我已經脫離唔到腦魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腦魔，已經存活喺我每個細胞之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2486217c727aa9228570bd86d516331765c8f60f","tid":1102081,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:41:55.000Z","msg":"今日青山走犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc2f58e9a80004269f96fb0850bc4aad056cd5a","tid":1102081,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2486217c727aa9228570bd86d516331765c8f60f","tid